@EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress = https://localhost:7113

### Demo - Default version (v1)
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/Demo
Accept: application/json

### Demo - URL Segment Versioning v1
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Demo
Accept: application/json

### Demo - URL Segment Versioning v2
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/v2/Demo
Accept: application/json

### Demo - Header Versioning v1
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/Demo
Accept: application/json
x-api-version: 1

### Demo - Header Versioning v2
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/Demo
Accept: application/json
