### Demo - Query String Versioning v1
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/Demo?api-version=1
Accept: application/json

### Demo - Query String Versioning v2
GET {{EndpointsSwaggerVersioning_HostAddress}}/api/Demo?api-version=2
Accept: application/json

### Demo - Media Type Versioning v1
